  Consider the following route configuration:
  
  ```
  @RouteConfig({
    path: '/user', component: UserCmp, alias: 'user'
  });
  class MyComp {}
  ```
  
  When linking to a route, you can write:
  
  ```
  <a router-link="user">link to user component</a>
  ```
  
